The paper proposes a new method for reinforcement learning, specifically for improving the soft-actor-critic algorithm. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The paper also deals with continuous control tasks, which suggests that it may belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) and Systems and Control (cs.SY) categories. Additionally, the paper mentions using a function approximator for representing policies, which is a common technique in Computer Vision (cs.CV).
